@model ForgotPassword
@{
	Layout = "_Layout.txt.cshtml";
}
Hi,

You requested your password to be reset for @Url.Absolute(string.Empty). If you did not make this request, please ignore this email. If you did make this request just click the link below:

@Url.Absolute(Url.Account().ResetPassword(Model.Token))

If the above URL does not work try copying and pasting it into your browser. If you continue to have problem please contact us on @ConfigurationManager.AppSettings["Email:Support"] and we'll help you out!.